metadata.name: All Dogs Go to Heaven
metadata.description: Greg Aime' , Hatian-American digital collagist uses Clintons love of dog imagery as amply displayed in all of his early work as a signature. He uses select pedigree dogs and the royalty of the funk, gold leashes alongside ones of God's angels looking down as they play. He imagines where all of Clintons dogs (work) would arrive at their final resting place.
